## Additional Terms for Game Memory Reading

This software is designed to read game memory for educational and personal use.
Users are responsible for ensuring their use complies with:

1. The game's End User License Agreement (EULA)
2. Platform terms of service (Steam, etc.)
3. Local laws and regulations regarding software modification

The software is intended for single-player use with the DS3 Fog Randomizer mod
and streaming/recording purposes. Use responsibly and ethically.

